<p>
  <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/">Eleventy</a> has a very powerful <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/docs/plugins/navigation/">Navigation Plugin</a> for rendering N-depth menus, breadcrumbs, and other navigational tools. "What other kids of navigation tools," you may ask? We can also use
  the plugin to render JSON-LD for a page's <a href="https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList">schema.org BreadcrumbList</a>. Including this structured data on pages may enrich their experiences on Google Search Engine Result Pages (SERPs).
</p>
<!-- excerpt -->

<p>
